When tou want to use next image as background, use fill, object fit cover, sizes="100vw" placeholder="blur"
sizes: telling next js not to use unnecessary images based on viewport when using fill

quality: 100

placeholder: used for only local images

using relative parent: you should give the wrapping div height i.e when building cards

2. Use avif and webP formats for better speed
   images: {
   formats: ["image/avif", "image/webp"],
   remotePatterns: [
   {
   protocol: "https",
   hostname: "image.mux.com",
   },
   ],
   },
